name: Red Alert
description:
Airplane mid-air, passengers getting up, flight attendant making sure all the storage bins are closed, suddenly the ambience turns red.

It's an alien spaceship hijacking the plane electronics. No one knows what's going to happen. The super-advanced aliens are also controlling the minds of the passengers. Everyone is strangely unaware of what is about to happen.

The pilots may already be unconscious. 
Fasten your seatbelts!
